{"tid":279852,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"〈單機, 行山〉鹿兒島,霧島,屋久島 8日點夠玩....","createTime":"2017-06-11T15:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T14:03:40.000Z","uid":113843,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"739b28f3c2dfb6c56b609c14d6085c2c37cc66be","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"係一個風和日麗既春天, 我搭上左飛往鹿兒島既航班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實, 與其話去鹿兒島, 不如話, 我係想去<strong>屋久島</strong>!<br />\n(得8日, 淨係玩屋久島都唔夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>屋久島</strong>係日本最早被立入世界自然遺產既地方<br />\n島上面既森林同生態物種古老而豐富, 島上最著名既杉樹林有數千年既歷史, 經歷過伐木時期, 現時已經進入盡力保育既年代<br />\n宮崎駿既幽靈公主/魔法公主亦係以屋久島作為藍本<br />\n<br />\n由於地理問題, 位於九州最南部既屋久島長年降雨<br />\n甚至有一個月落35日雨既講法<br />\n所以整個行程為左追求屋久島既藍天而將其放左係最尾<br />\n<strong>行程如下</strong>(day):<br />\n鹿兒島市(2) -&gt; 指宿(1) -&gt; 霧島(2) -&gt; 屋久島(3)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>劇透:</strong><br />\n<strong>櫻島</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/3/2894/34024168130_47d4ee7630_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F3%2F2894%2F34024168130_47d4ee7630_b.jpg&h=1435ed1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>霧島</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4262/35072677782_41c91e76ea_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4262%2F35072677782_41c91e76ea_b.jpg&h=0b419e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>屋久島</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4289/35238203345_c182179fab_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4289%2F35238203345_c182179fab_b.jpg&h=2c200966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>屋久島</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4254/35108402731_5595e0f2ac_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4254%2F35108402731_5595e0f2ac_b.jpg&h=a74875b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36eb0dacdd4c2d1d9bf06720dcdb9d50d60870b","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:31:31.000Z","msg":"ig一時時會update: <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/hesitated_life\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhesitated_life&d=jOKTudGZlBM%2FQs1%2FraDNKzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7462fe4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/hesitated_life</a>"},{"pid":"47c5c56b08a7fecc2313679e6c77bd8e02c44d1c","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">DAY1 鹿兒島市</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n到步後第一日, 迎接我既係雨天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由於打算盡量登山, 所以唯有將非登山行程盡量放係呢日<br />\n<br />\n由於大多登山地點位處偏遠, 因此此行大部份日子均為自駕<br />\n早上由機場租車後, 驅車直落鹿兒島市<br />\n第一站: <strong>鹿兒島水族館</strong><br />\n<br />\n或者因為睇住D水中生物游下游下好治癒,<br />\n參觀水族館差不多已經成為去旅行既指定動作<br />\n鹿兒島水族館好細, 分左做上下兩三層<br />\n但係佈局同埋打理得幾好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4216/35073695682_8c29a8b519_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4216%2F35073695682_8c29a8b519_b.jpg&h=e765a99c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4244/35073695482_04d7f22301_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4244%2F35073695482_04d7f22301_b.jpg&h=1d4510ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4261/35073700022_dc9221b304_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4261%2F35073700022_dc9221b304_b.jpg&h=df7d5712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4243/35199086256_789a2773f0_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4243%2F35199086256_789a2773f0_b.jpg&h=51a25203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係水族館避雨hea左一個上午後, 天色仍然好差<br />\n鹿兒島市實在無咩室內活動好做<br />\n於是就去左<strong>鹿兒島中央商場</strong><br />\n行左幾個圏後無咩好買.....落後地方......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4255/35199089886_eaf753a3e5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4255%2F35199089886_eaf753a3e5_b.jpg&h=3a7865ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於天色灰昏, 無咩心機, 決定提早渣車落指宿浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個天仲係咁衰<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4278/35199116726_b2c39ca03c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4278%2F35199116726_b2c39ca03c_b.jpg&h=bb528475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一日就係灰朦朦既細雨下結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>(續...)</strong>"},{"pid":"0390e25bf2e31f0fb11afdf89648bae6463ae37e","tid":279852,"uid":97904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T17:27:26.000Z","msg":"櫻島幅相好撚靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73817998c01dae0cf92aef178f2e64d2615710e6","tid":279852,"uid":47376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T17:37:48.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\nBtw樓主用咩機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"17deac28ba0d8d9e1e7245b1fc5838e14ba39e22","tid":279852,"uid":49745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T17:41:51.000Z","msg":"9月去 留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee55053e7daf04d3b35047c