852,"uid":25491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:29:12.000Z","msg":"留名 25號去 鹿兒島入褔岡出 九日<br />\n仲諗緊去唔去屋久島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff846ff9176fb2c00d4e62aa4f981ccac7934d4","tid":279852,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T08:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名 25號去 鹿兒島入褔岡出 九日<br />\n仲諗緊去唔去屋久島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9日既話去埋啦"},{"pid":"20aadc33a689ebe1e752187b64b526c0f6ae07ee","tid":279852,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"單機自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以講下租車"},{"pid":"9701d108af636708dfc86fa502e73d30afd0cf76","tid":279852,"uid":32012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"D相好靚<br />\n巴打一個人自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"090bb001f121f15475237ef46f1ec65cf325cd69","tid":279852,"uid":44550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T08:34:44.000Z","msg":"留名  巴打係幾月去  想出年年中去  起碼3d2n屋久島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59abbaab1f013934957902d5190b9d074ba25ea","tid":279852,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:56:20.000Z","msg":"好想去"},{"pid":"a0cf24d6b6c672b6b0eec88ef1c3d0961b5cb3ed","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好靚<br />\n有興趣參考行程, 但唔識渣車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識渣車真係好難去d偏遠地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n的士貴到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3472d84d50775f88b66d79bb59081f3586038dea","tid":279852,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"寫detail d 唔該"},{"pid":"b5b828e400bb7e6d59a3e6532a289f82fa5b448b","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T12:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名 25號去 鹿兒島入褔岡出 九日<br />\n仲諗緊去唔去屋久島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9日既話去埋啦</blockquote><br />\n最最起碼2個full day, 唔係有d浪費<br />\n其實而家熊本城未重建好, 阿蘇又爆完, 上福岡中間都無乜停留點..."},{"pid":"911795e0170c0491e73bd9e8ffc067f1ee7e506a","tid":279852,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T12:23:42.000Z","msg":"屋久島正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d9e61012b2d113a08e9236e82897bd2713e593","tid":279852,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好靚<br />\n有興趣參考行程, 但唔識渣車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識渣車真係好難去d偏遠地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n的士貴到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係唔識渣車 所以上次無去依啲地方 唯一遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cc9dfdba3bebc749cc3102c03602ce2f4984ce","tid":279852,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"正喎 <br />\n我7月都去 <br />\n有無邊度多野買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27461c114eac85150d617de9b2ee85e05bf4db3","tid":279852,"uid":102009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"巴打 有無去開聞岳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac918be286d0be8eedc3170614285d80db4bd867","tid":279852,"uid":87493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"你d相影得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f40c6a56e55c736a7479a77305af1ae41eb8fc0","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">DAY2 指宿</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日, 我施施然訓到9點, 結果被旅館既餐廳打黎叫我快D落去食早餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完個早餐, 天色昏暗多雲, 悠閒地整理左行李後正式出發<br />\n<br />\n指宿最著名既活動係砂浴, 係用溫泉水加熱既熱砂將你埋住, 等你焗返一身汗既玩法。但係天氣實在有D凍,要除衫............不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是呼, 我向住南邊既海岸出發。係途中, 路過<strong>流水麵</strong>既發源地 - <strong>唐船峽</strong><br />\n呢度使用唐船峽既泉水, 加上現代化既機械流水轉兜, 將麵條放落水度轉下轉下, 撈返上黎沾D豉油蔥花, 就係唐船峽流水麵<br />\n當我黎到呢度既時候只係11點, 成間店舖只有3,4個人。一個套餐包左一兜麵, 一條燒魚, 一碟魚生, 兩舊飯團。老實講, 呢度D麵無乜特別, D水同普通水一樣無味, 玩左一陣之後, 發現最好食係條魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4203/34440208374_e60334a157_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4203%2F34440208374_e60334a157_b.jpg&h=f92574af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4219/35154004321_5171ce44aa_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4219%2F35154004321_5171ce44aa_b.jpg&h=00113304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指宿位處海邊, 沿住海岸有大量景點, 知林島, 薩摩長崎鼻, 動物園, 潘所鼻等等基本上可以玩2日。不過毋忘初衷, 既然旅程目標為登山, 飲飽食醉後, 立即劍指<strong>開聞岳</strong>!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>開聞岳</strong>係位於指宿最南既火山, 佢既形態同周邊既風光令佢被稱為薩摩富士山。高度924m既佢, 步行上山來回需時約5小時。大部份步道尚算平緩, 除左最後既一段比較陡峭, 算係相當易行。<br />\n<br />\n網絡示意圖(轉貼):<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ibusuki.or.jp/tourism/assets_c/2016/01/23_1-thumb-420xauto-9261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibusuki.or.jp%2Ftourism%2Fassets_c%2F2016%2F01%2F23_1-thumb-420xauto-9261.jpg&h=152f8bc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旅客中心, 天氣仍然灰朦朦<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4244/34440203874_f56152bd4d_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4244%2F34440203874_f56152bd4d_b.jpg&h=2e7dd89e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條路幾易行, 但係9成時間都係樹林入面行<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4269/34440200084_6cf5ba57e5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4269%2F34440200084_6cf5ba57e5_b.jpg&h=a6af7ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[突發] 係陽光呀!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4240/35154000521_6d274581ed_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4240%2F35154000521_6d274581ed_b.jpg&h=7a86c323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於到頂! 走出樹林之後豁然開朗, 去到山頂除左有返藍天白雲, 仲有一個180度既鹿兒島景!<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4211/35243668196_5c5d5f244e_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4211%2F35243668196_5c5d5f244e_b.jpg&h=76fb76b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4203/35153981021_db72048776_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4203%2F35153981021_db72048776_b.jpg&h=2a70093d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4208/35243661416_6bf8a670e3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4208%2F35243661416_6bf8a670e3_b.jpg&h=7325b8d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一邊望返東面, 可以見倒突左出黎既就係長崎鼻<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4257/35243676116_5e4241dcd0_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4257%2F35243676116_5e4241dcd0_b.jpg&h=03052f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>賽後檢討:</strong><br />\n開聞岳頂雖然有無敵景觀, 但沿途都係樹林入面無咩野睇, 所以整體黎講算係幾悶。建議大家去下長崎鼻之類既地方, 由低處欣賞開聞岳會比較化算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩完開聞岳後已經日落, 聽日開始將會進入好天氣時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正好去<strong>霧島</strong>登山！ 為此, 我由鹿兒島南面既指宿漏夜飛車, 直達北面既霧島<br />\n<br />\n今晚浸個靚溫泉, 聽日就登霧島山!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4282/35243669076_dea59cd79e_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4282%2F35243669076_dea59cd79e_b.jpg&h=2b203386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒店大堂條電梯....欺騙我感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4237/35153985071_ac80bae05f_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4237%2F35153985071_ac80bae05f_b.jpg&h=70b88c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(待續...)"},{"pid":"d2a2c95c08ceafc2f4e278ff4decb70004478bac","tid":279852,"uid":11736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"留名，個景好撚靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fe91b4844c4da0e7482cd9cdf4e3d1e9c309e9","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 有無去開聞岳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一講就黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過回顧返成個旅程, 開聞岳真係輸曬.."},{"pid":"ad7036ece3ee295a9821151a0cc19ca8e0d8d3c5","tid":279852,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打 有無去開聞岳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一講就黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過回顧返成個旅程, 開聞岳真係輸曬..</blockquote><br />\n行山緊係唔去開聞岳<br />\n開聞岳用黎睇架ma<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea79e0d5e20e1f56645c3cbc85ee29efb7d9a273","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單機自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以講下租車</blockquote><br />\n租車黎講我次次都用樂天, 感覺上平過曬其他(我有幾平租幾平) <br />\n暫時未遇過話唔租比外國人, 車既質素都唔差<br />\n但係有一個例外, 就係屋久島<br />\n屋久島有d本地居民開既租車鋪, 會平過其他勁多, 因為我本來無諗住係屋久島渣車, 後來改左計劃, 旅客中心介紹左個好好人既租車公司姐姐比我, 先知原來咁平<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 咁岩果個禮拜屋久島好少人,"},{"pid":"481c52edaeb39efb19d17b71f9a14df4f1eac333","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打 有無去開聞岳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一講就黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過回顧返成個旅程, 開聞岳真係輸曬..</blockquote><br />\n行山緊係唔去開聞岳<br />\n開聞岳用黎睇架ma<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyes <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中伏"},{"pid":"32b76bb06c401065ecf9f9197252280feee0bcd4","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D相好靚<br />\n巴打一個人自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\nyup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0602422583440784ec961f965936ec0de4271434","tid":279852,"uid":32012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>D相好靚<br />\n巴打一個人自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\nyup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n攪到我都想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n八日租左幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class