s=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSo sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64fa1969214fdc3e95acac88d342706069d8db0","tid":279852,"uid":65234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我嘅目標都係每次旅行去唔同嘅水族館同動物園<br />\n望住佢地游黎游去真係身心舒暢<br />\n巴打去過沖繩嘅水族館未？<br />\n<br />\nBtw食流水麵係個打邊爐嘅爐入面食真係好無癮</blockquote><br />\n流水麵去高千穗好似有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似期間限定 夏天先有"},{"pid":"da60772c29ef81e9b9b8e403a31b2ab43b0d33ac","tid":279852,"uid":65234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我嘅目標都係每次旅行去唔同嘅水族館同動物園<br />\n望住佢地游黎游去真係身心舒暢<br />\n巴打去過沖繩嘅水族館未？<br />\n<br />\nBtw食流水麵係個打邊爐嘅爐入面食真係好無癮</blockquote><br />\n去左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n塊玻璃真係好大, 但係亦都好多人, 無左種悠閒感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出面個海好美麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最想去沖繩個水族館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打暫時最推介邊到嘅水族館？"},{"pid":"8eb3b9926e6283addcd8f03369a44bf95c08afd8","tid":279852,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:01:25.000Z","msg":"啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac20a948ece13019b1983d74751f7664bd2e28d6","tid":279852,"uid":59666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"F5"},{"pid":"b23d1320e15291feca6ed59b967036b651979b99","tid":279852,"uid":34993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:04:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5XIiep2D1Dk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5XIiep2D1Dk&d=jOKTudGZlBM%2FQs1%2FraDNKzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=03b60a0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5XIiep2D1Dk</a>"},{"pid":"6bf38a316a89cfc09b8dee8b02f46f9d37306606","tid":279852,"uid":34395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開聞岳難度係點？同香港啲山比例？如馬鞍山大金鐘？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"47ee416e3d5baea2f91e4e693a2c1dfc6ac22b12","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開聞岳難道係點？同香港啲山比例如馬鞍山大金鐘？</blockquote><br />\n獅子山都比多佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好易行"},{"pid":"5bd29c17a9e4d9f1b1f805e37e438f0c135f35a3","tid":279852,"uid":51361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:44:59.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"74cc1485534c5412146a8c6cb11b577886b22271","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">DAY3 霧島山 (上)<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三天。天還未光已經起床。<br />\n為既, 就係在霧島山山脊上走一遍<br />\n<br />\n<strong>霧島山</strong>由一連串火山口所組成, 大大少少既火山峰及火山湖遍佈整個區域。中間最高既韓國岳高1700米, 據說係好天既時候, 係山頂可以眺望韓國而得名。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;霧島山連峰(轉貼from wiki)<br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/24/Kirishima_from_Maruoka_2.jpg/1200px-Kirishima_from_Maruoka_2.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F2%2F24%2FKirishima_from_Maruoka_2.jpg%2F1200px-Kirishima_from_Maruoka_2.jpg%22&d=jOKTudGZlBM%2FQs1%2FraDNKzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=35d9098e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/24/Kirishima_from_Maruoka_2.jpg/1200px-Kirishima_from_Maruoka_2.jpg&quot;</a> alt=&quot;Kirishima from Maruoka 2.jpg&quot;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n霧島山既交通相當困難, 巴士班次每日大約只有兩班。即使我自駕, 亦難以配合巴士時間返回出發點取車。因此, 我決定於<strong>Ebino高原</strong>起步, 登上韓國岳, 然後沿山脊步行至<strong>高千穗河原</strong>, 再飛的返回Ebino高原(聽講約7000yen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4208/34595573473_eb1a3439df_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4208%2F34595573473_eb1a3439df_b.jpg&h=fcebc640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是, 我帶上幾個係family mart買既飯糰, 就往Ebino高原出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於酒店停車場<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4278/34562621424_4a7c3ae1bc_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4278%2F34562621424_4a7c3ae1bc_b.jpg&h=cece84b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半小時左右到達Ebino高原停車場<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4275/34562603614_181cffe9e9_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4275%2F34562603614_181cffe9e9_b.jpg&h=7ee1c90c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始登山! 開始既路段為斜路, 相對平坦<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4200/35405064465_33a6519ec8_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4200%2F35405064465_33a6519ec8_b.jpg&h=97b07c0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走不多遠即見到冒煙既硫磺山<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4231/34595591233_b56e589b26_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4231%2F34595591233_b56e589b26_b.jpg&h=79c1271b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20分鐘後, Ebino高原已在遠遠的腳下 (紅色屋)<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4219/34595588873_e58d7c6d89_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4219%2F34595588873_e58d7c6d89_b.jpg&h=a5231e87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後, 係約1-2小時既梯級, 碎石及結冰既土地。呢一段算係最辛苦既一段, 由山腳一直上到韓國岳頂端為止。回望一下, 不知不覺間已提升了很多<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4232/34595583553_86671aaee4_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4232%2F34595583553_86671aaee4_b.jpg&h=ad4eb0a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到頂喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4216/35405132045_cc3e466e0c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4216%2F35405132045_cc3e466e0c_b.jpg&h=cc378032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4273/34562607104_d67a689baa_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4273%2F34562607104_d67a689baa_b.jpg&h=3feaacf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國岳火山口<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4279/34595561103_7cf5af6038_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4279%2F34595561103_7cf5af6038_b.jpg&h=92350669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要休息一下, 山頂只有零下幾度, 加上超級大風, 山頂雖靚但卻不宜久留<br />\n寶礦力不如請我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4200/34595566343_cc0439cdba_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4200%2F34595566343_cc0439cdba_b.jpg&h=c382b730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4216/34595568903_52a60ac150_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4216%2F34595568903_52a60ac150_b.jpg&h=d6ce0a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四圍張望一下<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4252/34595554243_86004975f5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4252%2F34595554243_86004975f5_b.jpg&h=cadb4f88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係呢個時候, 發現指標柱上面掛住一張告示, 原來<strong>新燃岳</strong>處於活躍期, 因此新燃岳2km直徑範圍都列為禁區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無辦法, 還好韓國岳山頂除左往新燃岳方向外, 尚有另一條路通往<strong>大浪池</strong>, 未至於要走回頭路下山<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4286/34595572843_f255745b86_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4286%2F34595572843_f255745b86_b.jpg&h=9522047a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n往大浪池出發<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4260/34595550323_18011a3cdf_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4260%2F34595550323_18011a3cdf_b.jpg&h=1d5fd72a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越黎越近<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4266/34595548203_cab42fb7a8_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4266%2F34595548203_cab42fb7a8_b.jpg&h=822f3b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4251/35275460281_0f6babfcfe_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4251%2F35275460281_0f6babfcfe_b.jpg&h=f3289e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經過大浪池後, 轉往Ebino高原方向走, 一路都係好清爽既山林。 Ebino高原附近全部都係呢種唔會好密既樹林, 遍地綠色, 通爽之餘亦令人心情愉快<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4255/34595578993_8ec9925c8f_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4255%2F34595578993_8ec9925c8f_b.jpg&h=276402d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後, 經歷4,5小時後返回Ebino高原。因緣濟會下慳返7000yen, 但就無辦法行倒高千穗峰(聽聞好靚)。久未運動加上連續兩天登山, 雖然時間只係中午, 呢個時候都係返酒店浸個露天溫泉, 舒緩呢幾日既疲勞, 下午繼續出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHi 酒店, Hi 噴氣地區<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4196/34595570863_c3cc711389_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4196%2F34595570863_c3cc711389_b.jpg&h=78e4f695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>(續....)</strong>"},{"pid":"eec4fb92182ba0d7a907709c081eaee61209f99b","tid":279852,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"啲相好靚呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去左兩次鹿兒島都未去屋久島 下次真係要去了"},{"pid":"7f606b1e1b821b86f18ada09428509bafcdfaf4d","tid":279852,"uid":113843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260427a94ee93f5b850baf00889739c9c88743be","tid":279852,"uid":56055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe7ae437ae62932a0c5dd7831818a69e953bd6a","tid":279852,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T21:24:35.000Z","msg":"屋久島 識玩！<br />\n果邊好撚靚 去左6日 好掛住果邊既天氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚晚都好多星 又靜"},{"pid":"fa15d88f76fc8e9170c9b9a5a2102f3c84a8e0e0","tid":279852,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T21:34:13.000Z","msg":"好彩老豆係屋久島做野我襯sem break 過去搵下佢先知有個咁靚既地方<br />\n人又少破壞又少<br />\n成個島連m記7仔都冇間 得一間mos burger<br />\n完完全全遠離煩囂 因為連上網都好撚慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後去到每一到都好似上緊geog堂咁<br />\n最衰我唔中意行山<br />\n行完白谷雲水峽都唔覺有咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/053054_40c1e491b87eea1b1ffa3b08c2882051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F053054_40c1e491b87eea1b1ffa3b08c2882051.jpg&h=caea2f12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n送上一張係春田濱影出去影既相<br />\n利申用電話影加上唔識影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a27afa1b0d91f9dd39de0bee3ee718271806746","tid":279852,"uid":48054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T22:40:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a311fcb4f5acb3c8e7d00f623275552f0b7d5813","tid":279852,"uid":48054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T22:42:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a33e79ba5ab3df26377352054397c85450de23d2","tid":279852,"uid":78313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:14:13.000Z","msg":"巴打幾多月去<br />\n個天幾靚"},{"pid":"e66d81ee4c04d637a4450ead1bf9180bca2e94c3","tid":279852,"uid":68225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:55:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5d4791888635a80f1211cb15827624ef04a9bbfd","tid":279852,"uid":38131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:03:52.000Z","msg":"係屋久島上面真係超超超級開心<br />\n果種生活同埋果個靚景<br />\n留係左上面7日 但都係覺得唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903bb4daa32294f3c3b608af7a2218990ffbdff7","tid":279852,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"巴打我下星期會去,有兩日會係鹿兒島 只係買左pass有咩地方好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5414aacb79f9d96689f5f3fdb32e80a0e272e57","tid":279852,"uid":65708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T04:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係屋久島上面真係超超超級開心<br />\n果種生活同埋果個靚景<br />\n留係左上面7日 但都係覺得唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過天氣實在太飄忽"},{"pid":"c7f86f870f2edb77c794ada45d77f90c5990cf30","tid":279852,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T04:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係屋久島上面真係超超超級開心<br />\n果種生活同埋果個靚景<br />\n留係左上面7日 但都係覺得唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過天氣實在太飄忽</blockquote><br />\n係既 但日日揸車都仲過得去 同埋係條街落雨都好行既"},{"pid":"125e390ab0ca342bf5386873939570dee5d6d46b","tid":279852,"uid":65708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係屋久島上面真係超超超級開心<br />\n果種生活同埋果個靚景<br />\n留係左上面7日 但都係覺得唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過天氣實在太飄忽</blockquote><br />\n係既 但日日揸車都仲過得去 同埋係條街落雨都好行既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屋久島自駕遊真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己覺得最正都係行山，太鼓岩個風景真係好迷人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63787b01e890fbf3bddd57b60966f1aed10ae2ca","tid":279852,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7019d0bff068756b1f9ab0798efb7bb7d73fac8b","tid":279852,"uid":70003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"諗住冬天出發去屋久島<br />\n會唔會危險？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875ac228f69b8dce80e1a15d0276f9867d641e1d","tid":279852,"uid":40207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b791530dc9560d4f68c8cccd8f431f1054895b24","tid":279852,"uid":54232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"63c952c3449e788e21456f2fecf96f19b932fee8","tid":279852,"uid":65708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住冬天出發去屋久島<br />\n會唔會危險？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會啦，大把人住島上冬天咪照住<br />\n不過行山就麻煩d同凍好多，如果加埋落雨就真係要注意保暖，而且冬天有d巴士路線或班次會暫停"},{"pid":"b99cb4cdde9915333506df7d9db31e409be852fa","tid":279852,"uid":52560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"高質留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}